txt.en: Your mission is to kill spiders in Ushbarab and slay the Matron of the Fang when she emerges to defend her nest.\n\nSpeak with Raphûz to travel.
'Thank you for dealing with the beasts in Ushbarab.\n\n'Travellers will have one less thing to worry about now when passing by, even if it is only temporary.'
You have successfully defeated the Matron of the Fang in Ushbarab! Return with the scout to Raphûz with this report.
'Your task is clear, [placeholder], travel to Ushbarab and slay spiders until the matron emerges, then defeat the Matron of the Fang.'
Your mission is to kill spiders in Ushbarab and slay the Matron of the Fang when she emerges to defend her nest.
There is no twist in this mission.

'Greetings, [placeholder]. The coalition has put out a call here in Ub Nishir to cull the matron in the nest to the north-west, known as Ushbarab. The spiders there grow more foetid and strong and they can not be allowed to remain. Please travel there and clear out what you can and be sure to slay the matron.'
